long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SAFEQ Cloud printing for Chromebooks and Chrome OS

This Chrome extension allow you to print to available SAFEQ Cloud printers.

Both secure print (requiring authentication at the device) and direct print queues can be enabled.

This extension can be used with SAFEQ Cloud and EveryonePrint Mobile
